{"story":{"group_1":[{"armatureList":[{"animation":["action"],"armatureId":1,"filePath":"resource/image_native/effect/story/general/3507_film_frame.ExportJson","zOrder":"messageBack"}],"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_23181.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200904,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/mt_calender_day-xx.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"nameNarration":"","narration":"[surround:8026_doorbell]*Jingle* *Jingle*","narrationBg":"bg_adv_23181.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"autoTurnNoDelay":1,"chara":[{"id":200904,"voiceFull":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-1"}],"nameAvCenter":"Mabayu","narrationEffect":"out","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]Welcome... Oh?","textAvColor":"textMabayu"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200904}]},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":200904,"pos":0,"voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-1"}],"textAvClear":1},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime07","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":0,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-2"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Hello."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200904,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-3"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So, how did it go today?"},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-4"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Our new recruit is very reliable, so with@your advice, she's been doing well."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-6"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]She's particularly powerful@when it comes to attacks."},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"autoTurnNoDelay":1,"chara":[{"id":200501,"motion":1,"voiceFull":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-7"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Raining molten gold onto enemies...@Definitely not the kind of ability you@want to be on the wrong side of."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200501}]},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200904,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-8","voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-7"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Ohh, nice. That's good."},{"chara":[{"id":200904,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-9"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Gotta make sure our newbie picks up@my slack."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200904,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-10"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]While you guys do that,@I'll be doing my best serving cakes."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200501,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-11"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]......"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200904,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-12"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Hm? Is something wrong?"},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"lipSynch":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-13"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]It's just... There is something@that's been bothering me."},{"chara":[{"id":200904,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-14"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Like what?"},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-15"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]You know how she became rich@from her wish, right?"},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-16"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]She seemed really happy at first..."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-17"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But lately, things seem to be@getting a little bit out of hand..."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-18"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]If people don't listen to her, she immediately@resorts to money to solve problems."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200904,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-19"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Hmm, I see..."},{"chara":[{"id":200904,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-20"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Getting your wish granted doesn't@necessarily lead to happiness, huh..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-21"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Now, I have something to discuss."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-22"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I'm thinking that it's time to@reveal your existence to her."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200904,"motion":400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-23"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]You're really going to tell her...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-24"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Lately, she's been curious about how@I manage to give her such precise commands."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-25"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I'd like to explain it all to her properly@at this point."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200904,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-26"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Seriously...?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200501,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-27"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]We can't just keep secrets@from a trusted ally forever."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-28"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Are you nervous...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_060.exp3.json","id":200904,"motion":400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-29"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20][chara:200904:effect_shake]Of course I am!@I suck at socializing."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-30"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]It'll be fine. You manage to talk@with me normally, don't you?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200904,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-31"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]You don't get it!"},{"chara":[{"id":200904,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-32"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I have no problem casually hanging out@with people AFTER we're already friends!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200904,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-33"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]The real problem is that first step!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-34"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]...You seem to understand yourself,@at least."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-35"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But I think it's very important for her@to know there are other allies out there..."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-36"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So please, Mabayu!"},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-37"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Become her friend,@and listen to her problems!"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200904,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913007-001-38"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Mnnnhhh..."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"deleteArmatureList":[1],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
